downloadTitle: Dynamics 365 for Field Service Automation Sample Data v3
downloadDescription: The Field Service sample data package installs the "Fabrikam Manufacturing Master Data" (v3.0.0.0) solution with approximately 1.3k records across ~30 entities.
detailsSection:
To become familiar with Dynamics 365 for Field Service, it's useful to have a small, pre-configured dataset that makes it easy to trace through end to end scenarios.

For this purpose, we've created a seperate sample data installation package (English-language only at this time) that makes it easier to explore and learn about FS.
Running this install performs the following:
1) The package will provide setup data which will default behaviour of Field Service
2) Imports sample data such as Bookable Resources, Roles and other reference data.

IMPORTANT: Currently, there is no way to un-install this sample data. This should only be used on demonstration, evaluation, training and test systems.
installInstructionSection:
Please visit "https://aka.ms/fpsrefdata" for the latest and greatest instructions.
Download the self-extracting file, extract contents to a working folder and update the necessary configuration files as specified in the instructions in the PkgFolder sub-folder.
